Package org.sensorhub.api.datastore.obs

Class ObsFilter

java.lang.Object
org.sensorhub.api.datastore.obs.ObsFilter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Predicate<IObsData>, IQueryFilter
public class ObsFilter extends Object implements IQueryFilter, Predicate<IObsData>

Immutable filter object for observations.
There is an implicit AND between all filter parameters.
